{{!-- Daemonic Immunities badge (#143 — DH2 Errata L69-73).

     Rendered into the actor sheet header for actors carrying the
     Daemonic trait. Surfaces a crimson skull pill summarising the
     three immunities granted by the trait (disease / poison / Undying).
     The tooltip elaborates the once-per-session Undying rider.

     Context: rendered only when the parent template gates on
     `isDaemonic` — the partial assumes the gate has already fired
     and emits the badge unconditionally.

     Pure presentation: no actions, no data attributes, no event
     handlers. Composes with the underlying engine helpers in
     `src/module/rules/daemonic-immunities.ts`. --}}
<div class="wh40k-daemonic-immunities-badge tw-inline-flex tw-items-center tw-gap-1.5 tw-px-2 tw-py-1 tw-rounded-md tw-border tw-border-solid tw-border-crimson tw-bg-crimson/20 tw-text-crimson-light tw-text-[0.7rem] tw-font-bold tw-uppercase tw-tracking-wide tw-select-none"
     data-tooltip="{{localize "WH40K.DaemonicImmunities.Tooltip"}}"
     aria-label="{{localize "WH40K.DaemonicImmunities.BadgeLabel"}}">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-skull tw-text-crimson-light" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    <span class="wh40k-daemonic-immunities-badge__label">{{localize "WH40K.DaemonicImmunities.BadgeLabel"}}</span>
    <span class="wh40k-daemonic-immunities-badge__details tw-font-normal tw-normal-case tw-tracking-normal tw-opacity-90">
        {{localize "WH40K.DaemonicImmunities.DiseaseImmune"}} · {{localize "WH40K.DaemonicImmunities.PoisonImmune"}} · {{localize "WH40K.DaemonicImmunities.Undying"}}
    </span>
</div>
